issue.body:
@domoritz 

@mjskay Asked me to create this issue to ping you to do an accessibility review of this paper. As part of this issue, it might be helpful to log your process in a checklist, which we can use to create an issue template in the style of the [initial editor checklist](https://github.com/journalovi/2023-park-gatherplots/issues/new?assignees=&labels=pre-review&projects=&template=initial-editor-checklist.md&title=Initial+Editor+Checklist).

If possible, it would be helpful to have this in the next six weeks, to align with the overall review timeline.
Thanks!

